{"tid":1956322,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【自住驚閪】星展料今年樓價跌15%　負資產將慢慢浮現","createTime":"2020-04-03T06:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T11:11:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1f9671b79aab0b680ce275d10d54d9e7aee4d55e","tid":1956322,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T06:01:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518643-20200403.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518643-20200403.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=d86ef943\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518643-20200403.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3346f24f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518643-20200403.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1518643_1_L_20200403125328.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1518643_1_L_20200403125328.jpg&h=a6ae92e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n星展香港房地產業分析師丘卓文表示，本港住宅市場受社會事件及中美貿易戰影響，去年中開始步入下行周期，新型肺炎疫情下，今年上半年經濟無可避免收縮，第3季失業率預計升至5%。<br />\n<br />\n他說，上月金融市場波幅大，進一步影響購買力及需求，預計全年樓價下跌15%，豪宅表現更差。<br />\n<br />\n丘卓文相信，隨著經濟下行，負資產和斷供個案上升，但樓價不會重演金融海嘯和金融風暴式崩市，因為樓市辣招壓抑炒風，財務實力較差的市民難以買樓，加上未來2-3年供應不多，樓價顯著下跌機會較低。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，金融市場波動未如2008年第4季般大，預料負資產會慢慢浮現，情況不至於前兩次金融危機般嚴重。"},{"pid":"b3e1dbaa7d734c906d57ee36316a6f6c28d08947","tid":1956322,"uid":163207,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>信低置，唔怕！！！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4484f85bf47652f723adb57b804a1ef1b3e306c","tid":1956322,"uid":19092,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b3e1dbaa7d734c906d57ee36316a6f6c28d08947","tid":1956322,"uid":163207,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>信低置，唔怕！！！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T06:09:04.000Z","msg":"低置：我放租等人地幫我供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ffcdc095459435a90acea864a6064520c6586b","tid":1956322,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4484f85bf47652f723adb57b804a1ef1b3e306c","tid":1956322,"uid":19092,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b3e1dbaa7d734c906d57ee36316a6f6c28d08947","tid":1956322,"uid":163207,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>信低置，唔怕！！！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T06:09:04.000Z","msg":"低置：我放租等人地幫我供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T06:11:01.000Z","msg":"一直供到, 就唔會CALL LOAN！"},{"pid":"90d350d17844619774387914b843678d5039963e","tid":1956322,"uid":19092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a9ffcdc095459435a90acea864a6064520c6586b","tid":1956322,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4484f85bf47652f723adb57b804a1ef1b3e306c","tid":1956322,"uid":19092,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b3e1dbaa7d734c906d57ee36316a6f6c28d08947","tid":1956322,"uid":163207,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>信低置，唔怕！！！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T06:09:04.000Z","msg":"低置：我放租等人地幫我供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T06:11:01.000Z","msg":"一直供到, 就唔會CALL LOAN！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T06:11:56.000Z","msg":"信自己， 唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f149e0f131b161163ecc36458552f6665979a2e","tid":1956322,"uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T06:16:22.000Z","msg":"星展預測樓價將連跌3年 （2016/4/14）<br />\n<br />\n星展香港經濟研究部經濟師盧明俐表示，維持香港樓市今年下跌10%的預測。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n她又預期，樓市會跌2至3年，跌幅介乎10%至15%。樓市下跌主因並不是本港經濟崩潰，所以有別於金融風暴時的情形。她預計不同類型樓價會有差別，細價樓跌幅會較大。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n盧明俐又表示，內地經濟放緩，加上環球經濟動盪，香港難以維持全民就業，最快今年底至明年初，失業率會上升至4%。"},{"pid":"feb5dd9b35838f135b545f7a9d7e973e8125ca8b","tid":1956322,"uid":17866,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d4484f85bf47652f723adb57b804a1ef1b3e306c","tid":1956322,"uid":19092,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b3e1dbaa7d734c906d57ee36316a6f6c28d08947","tid":1956322,"uid":163207,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>信低置，唔怕！！！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T06:09:04.000Z","msg":"低置：我放租等人地幫我供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T07:36:50.000Z","msg":"屌你講到quote 我講咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccff12946081da3b2815d60813b7c18cbc641ef7","tid":1956322,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feb5dd9b35838f135b545f7a9d7